
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja-JP">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <title>エラー! - iamyukino.cn</title>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="https://iamyukino.cn/favicon.ico">
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/statics/as-includes/err/404.css">
    <script is:inline src="//iamyukino.cn/statics/as-includes/index/js/includes/jquery.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>

<div class="viewbox">
    <div class="error-page">
    <div class="content">
        <h1 data-text="404">404</h1>
        <br><br><br>
        <h4 data-text="Page not found">Page not found</h4>
        <p>お探しのページは削除、変更されたか、現在利用できない可能性があります</p>
        <p>問題があると思われる場合は、マシュマロでお知らせください</p>
        <p class="homelink" style="font-size:50%;"><br><a href="/">All</a> <a href="/">Rights</a> <a href="/">Reserved</a>. <a href="/">Copyright</a> <a href="/">©</a> <a href="/">2025</a> <a href="/">iamyukino.cn</a></p>
        <script>function back2lastdoc (){
            if (history.length > 1) window.history.go(-1);
            else window.location.href = '/';
        }</script>
        <div class="btns">
            <a onclick="back2lastdoc()">戻る</a>
            <a href="/ask">報告問題</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>
    <script>
        var patto = /^(?:https?:\/\/[^/]+)?\/ja-JP(?=\/|$|\?|#)/;
        var patt1 = /^(?:https?:\/\/[^/]+)?\/(zh((-|_)(HANS|HANT|TW|CHS|SG|MY|CHT|HK|MO|CN))?)(?=\/|$|\?|#)/i;
        var patt2 = /^(?:https?:\/\/[^/]+)?\/((ja|ko|en)((-|_)[A-Z]{2,3})?)(?=\/|$|\?|#)/i;
        if (patto.test(window.location.href))
            ;
        else if (patt1.test(window.location.href))
            window.location.href='/';
        else if (patt2.test(window.location.href))
            window.location.href='/ja-JP';
    </script>
</div>

<div class="iframe">
    <!--script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/eruda"></script>
    <script>eruda.init();</script-->
    <span id="iframe"></span>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="//iamyukino.cn/statics/as-includes/global/waifu/Samples/TypeScript/Demo/live2d/assets/waifu.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="//iamyukino.cn/statics/as-includes/global/js/aplayer/APlayer.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="//iamyukino.cn/statics/as-includes/global/js/iframe/iframe.css">
    <script is:inline data-swup-ignore-script src="//iamyukino.cn/statics/as-includes/global/js/iframe/iframe.js"></script>
</div>

</body>
</html>